data.description: Recently painted exterior, new furnace, new hot water heater, & new kitchen flooring. Drive up into the XL 2-Car garage. Stroll up the stairs & feel right at home as you step into the spacious Great Room. Warm fireplace to cozy up and relax. Steps away, a kitchen complete w/Stainless steel appliances. Enjoy a cup of coffee on the Balcony or sit & enjoy your favorite book. The basement has a Den/extra bedroom w/fireplace & living area. Large yard for entertaining, BBQ's or just enjoy your tranquil green space. Fully Fenced, Double gated, RV parking. Minutes to shopping, schools & freeways. New roof in the next 2 weeks.
